<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>No Results Found</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/public/css/styles.css">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .no-results-container {
            background: #fff;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            max-width: 500px;
            width: 100%;
        }

        .no-results-container h1 {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .no-results-container p {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .no-results-container a {
            text-decoration: none;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 16px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }

        .no-results-container a:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }

        .no-results-container .current-user {
            margin-top: 15px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #555;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="no-results-container">
        <h1>No Matches Found</h1>
        <p>We couldnâ€™t find any profiles that match your search criteria. Try modifying your search filters or exploring more options.</p>
        <a href="/search">Try Again</a>
        <p class="current-user">Logged in as: <strong><%= currentUser.name %></strong></p>
    </div>
</body>

</html>
